data.description: Have you ever wanted to own your own Airstrip? Look no further! This 60 acre property offers it all, licensed airstrip, Two big warehouse style barns, and a cozy "fly-in" cottage. The 1/1 cottage has all your necessities. The 2 Barns offer plenty of storage for just about anything and possibly an airplane or helicopter. Barn A is 72x56 and was used as a screened room assembly warehouse/business and Barn B is 49x42 and has been used to store misc. materials and equipment. The property is income producing and Ag exempt, it is being leased for haying, with easy access from either CR341 or NW 165th St. If this sounds like it checks all the boxes for you, come take a tour for yourself and see all this property has to offer.
